author: Minecraft
description:
*sniff, sniff* Do you smell waffles? It must be Netflix's Stranger Things DLC, just in time for the epic series finale!
  
Join “The Party” and play as your favorite character, like Will, Dustin, Mike, or Eleven. Characters' unique abilities will help you solve puzzles and vanquish foes. Hop on your bike and head to the Dressing Room for your free Hellfire Club T-shirt!
title: Minecraft x Stranger Things DLC
